description: CVCWVU Alumni Association Board presenting a $1,500 check to Matt Borman, Dir of Major Gifts for the Mountaineer Athletic Club (MAC), for annual membership ... the first WVU alumni chapter to join. Pictured from the left - Bob Whiteman, Al Dietz, Bob Jones, Matt Borman, Wayne Sparks, Carol Solan & Bob Basham. (Not pictured - Jeff Layne, Johnathon Kerr & Louise Seals)
